---

This project includes:
- Virtual Memory Simulator (CLI and Web versions)
- Interactive Educational Demo
- Comprehensive Test Suite
- Performance Analysis Tools
- Modern Web Interface with Animations
- Educational Content and Documentation

Educational Use: This software is specifically designed for educational purposes
in Operating Systems courses and Computer Science education. Feel free to use,
modify, and distribute for academic and learning purposes.

Academic Institution: BVRIT Hyderabad College of Engineering for Women
Course: Operating Systems (2024-25)
Team: Collaborative effort by passionate Computer Science students
